## âœ¨ What is Supervertaler?

Supervertaler is a **professional Computer-Aided Translation (CAT) editor** designed by a 30-year veteran translator for translators. It combines:

- ðŸ¤– **Multiple AI providers** - OpenAI GPT-4, Anthropic Claude, Google Gemini
- ðŸŽ¯ **Context-aware translation** - Full document understanding, figure context, translation memory
- ðŸ“š **Unified Prompt Library** - System Prompts (AI role) + Custom Instructions (user preferences)
- ðŸ†˜ **PDF Rescue** - AI-powered OCR for badly-formatted PDFs
- âœ… **Professional CAT features** - Segment editing, grid pagination, dual selection (memoQ-style)
- ðŸ”— **CAT tool integration** - memoQ, CafeTran, Trados Studio support
- ðŸ“Š **Smart auto-export** - Session reports, TMX, TSV, XLIFF, Excel
- ðŸ’¾ **Translation Memory** - Fuzzy matching with segment context

